    "zh": "💡 核心亮点：家庭友好设计 + 儿童水上乐园 + 米其林厨房 + 120㎡主人套房",
    "en": "💡 Core highlights: Family-friendly design + children’s water park + Michelin kitchen + 120㎡ master suite"
